data.description: This stunning 2016 build home located in the prestigious gated community of Shadow Lakes is now available for sale. The sellers upgraded the home with high end quartz counter tops throughout, luxury vynil flooring and stainless appliances. The two story home features 5 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with an office. The home has a spacious 2 car garage. Residents of the gorgeous, tranquil neighborhood can enjoy their own slice of Waterfront Wonderland near the coast of Southwest Florida in the Fort Myers area. Each home in this stunning community backs up to a body of water or a serene setting of the expansive nature preserve. Shadow Lakes offers residents both the convenience of living in a highly desired location along with beautiful, move-in ready homes. This new community offers breathtaking views right within the neighborhood and includes a playground, walking trails and easy access to State Road 82 and I-75 Shadow Lakes is the perfect place for home buyers in the Fort Myers area.
